{"tid":1781434,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連IOI都有空降閪...","createTime":"2019-12-13T06:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T11:59:49.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"744bf505586f9b072f75c3ee1cdf37a3a0278dc3","tid":1781434,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"[Mnet《PD101》第一季出道組I.O.I也造假了]13日據報導，根據之前《PD101》造假事件訴狀，檢察方提出是安俊英-金勇範PD等製作組個人謀劃造假，CJ是被害者。但在該節目第一季最後一期中，卻是其他製作組對I.O.I出道組排名進行了顛倒。可以說，此次事件不是個人行為，而是CJENM層面的結構性問題。<br />\n<br />\n而檢方對安俊英等不起訴的理由，則是在第一季最後直播的時候與觀眾投票不同，11位之外的B練習生與11位之內的A練習生調換，但安俊英表示自己當時自己是直播者，正在編輯拍攝部分進行播放業務，沒有負責投票結果統計業務，所以沒有捏造統計結果，並極力否認罪行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7014bd629abbc5f466b6c33aeff3add62ba6a2c9","tid":1781434,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"CJ是被害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbed266e9844087bd9660c2bffd2801195f35106","tid":1781434,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"Somi 世正...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f5ff85d374b5198259b61fde47faa05eac1172","tid":1781434,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cbed266e9844087bd9660c2bffd2801195f35106","tid":1781434,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:01:04.000Z","msg":"Somi 世正...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT